    "extras": [
      "Indian passport holders need a pre-arranged 9(a) tourist visa; current processing is roughly ₹2,500–₹3,500 plus insurance.",
      "November to April is the sweet spot; keep island-hopping days flexible because coast guard and WeatherPH advisories can cancel boats.",
      "Pre-book AirSwift sectors, Boracay hotel vouchers and holiday-period ferries well ahead for the best routing.",
      "Grab is the safest default for Manila and Cebu airport transfers, but cash is still useful for tricycles, vans and smaller island eateries.",
      "Oslob whale-shark tours are controversial; switch that Cebu day to Kawasan Falls or Moalboal if you want a lower-impact plan."
